            "width": 1500
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Add the<strong> beetroot wellingtons </strong>to one side of a <strong>baking paper</strong>-lined baking tray</p><p>Cut the <strong>remaining</strong> <strong>beetroot</strong> into wedges and add to the other side of the tray with the <strong>halved carrots</strong></p><p>Drizzle them with a little <strong>olive oil </strong>and a pinch of <strong>salt</strong></p><p>Put the tray in the oven for 30 min or until the pastry is golden and cooked through and the carrots are tender</p>",
      "order": 5,
      "media": {
