    {
      "instruction": "<p>Return the potatoes to a low heat with a knob of <strong>butter </strong>and a splash of <strong>milk </strong>and mash until smooth</p><p>Serve the <strong>beetroot wellington</strong> with the <strong>mash</strong> and <strong>roasted carrot</strong> <strong>& beetroot</strong> to the side</p><p>Pour over the <strong>onion gravy</strong></p><p>Enjoy!</p>",
